@using InquiryApp.Models;

@model Inquiry

@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<div>
    <h1>L&A Remodeling: Make Your Dream Home A Reality</h1>

    <h2>We Understand How Much Your Home Means to You</h2>

    <p>Your home is more than just a place to live. It’s where you create memories that last a lifetime, express your personality that 
        makes you unique, and enjoy your lifestyle that makes you happy. But over time, your home may start to look outdated, worn out, 
        or inefficient. You may have a vision of how your home could be, but you don’t know how to make it happen. You may want to 
        improve the functionality, appearance, or value of your home without breaking the bank. If you share any of these dreams, then 
        we would love to hear from you. We are L&A Remodeling, the home remodeling contractor who can turn your vision into reality.</p>

    <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>

    <p>We are not just a home remodeling contractor. We are a family-owned business that cares about quality, honesty, and customer 
        satisfaction. We have over 20 years of experience in the industry and we specialize in stairs, cabinets, wood flooring, decks, 
        attic ladders, and storage houses. We work with you to create custom designs that suit your needs and budget. We use high-quality 
        materials and products that will last for years. It is our pleasure to provide you with premier service and communication. That 
        means that we listen to your feedback, answer your questions, and keep you updated throughout the process. We have a satisfaction 
        guarantee policy that ensures that you are happy with the final result or we will fix it for free within the warranty period. 
        For more information, please see our Terms and Conditions page. We are grateful for the opportunity to work with you on your home 
        remodeling project. We appreciate your trust and confidence in us and we look forward to making your dream home a reality.</p>

    <h2>Our Services</h2>

    <p>We offer a wide range of home remodeling services to suit any taste, style, or budget. Whether you want to update your kitchen, 
        add more storage space, or enhance your outdoor living area, we can help you achieve your goals. Here are some of the services we 
        offer:</p>

    <h3>Stairs</h3>

    <p>We can design and install new stairs or repair and update existing ones. We can work with different materials, such as wood, 
        metal, or glass, and create various styles, such as straight, curved, spiral, or floating. We can also add safety features, such 
        as railings, handrails, or balusters.</p>

    <h3>Cabinets</h3>

    <p>We can design and install new cabinets or refinish and reface existing ones. We can work with different materials, such as wood, 
        laminate, or metal, and create various styles, such as modern, traditional, or rustic. We can also add features, such as drawers, 
        shelves, doors, or knobs.</p>

    <h3>Wood Flooring</h3>

    <p>We can install new wood flooring or repair and refinish existing ones. We can work with different types of wood, such as oak, 
        maple, or cherry, and create various finishes, such as glossy, matte, or distressed. We can also add features, such as borders, 
        inlays, or patterns.</p>

    <h3>Decks</h3>

    <p>We can design and build new decks or repair and maintain existing ones. We can work with different materials, such as wood, 
        composite, or vinyl, and create various shapes, sizes, and levels. We can also add features, such as railings, stairs, benches, 
        or planters. Decks are a great way to enhance your outdoor living area and enjoy the fresh air and sunshine. Whether you want to 
        create a cozy lounge, a dining area, or a play space, we can help you create the perfect deck for your home.</p>

    <h3>Attic Ladders</h3>

    <p>We can install new attic ladders or replace and adjust existing ones. We can work with different types of ladders, such as 
        folding, telescoping, or sliding. We can also add features, such as insulation, safety locks, or handles. Attic ladders are a 
        convenient and safe way to access your attic space and use it for storage or other purposes. Whether you want to save space, 
        increase security, or improve comfort, we can help you install the right attic ladder for your home.</p>

    <h3>Storage Houses</h3>

    <p>We can design and build new storage houses or repair and upgrade existing ones. We can work with different materials, such as 
        wood, metal, or plastic, and create various sizes and styles. We can also add features, such as windows, doors, shelves, or 
        hooks. Storage houses are a practical and attractive way to store your tools, equipment, or belongings outside your home. 
        Whether you want to organize your garage, protect your valuables, or create a hobby room, we can help you build the ideal 
        storage house for your needs.</p>

    @if (ViewBag.Message != null)
    {
        <div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
            @ViewBag.Message
        </div>
    }

    <div id="inquiry-form">
        <partial name="_InquiryForm" />
    </div>


</div>
